447
00:18:47,003 --> 00:18:48,129
EU ACHEI QUE VOCÊ FOSSE
MINHA AMIGA.

448
00:18:48,213 --> 00:18:49,214
EU SOU.

449
00:18:51,007 --> 00:18:52,800
(SUSPIRA EMOCIONALMENTE)

450
00:18:53,801 --> 00:18:55,637
